@RW.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:24110

### v1.0 — unprotected
GET {{RW.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1.0/authors
Accept: application/json

### v2.0 — registration
POST {{RW.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v2.0/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "alice",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstname": "Alice",
  "lastname": "A",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### v2.0 — login
POST {{RW.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v2.0/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "alice",
  "password": "password123"
}

### v2.0 — get authors with JWT
GET {{RW.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v2.0/authors
Authorization: Bearer <paste access_token here>

### v2.0 — current user
GET {{RW.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v2.0/authors/me
Authorization: Bearer <paste access_token here>

###
